      <example>
         <codeblock>&lt;linklist&gt;
  &lt;title&gt;Related tasks&lt;/title&gt;
  &lt;link href="debug.xml" type="task"&gt;&lt;/link&gt;
  &lt;link href="repair.xml" type="task"&gt;&lt;/link&gt;
  &lt;link href="test.xml" type="task"&gt;&lt;/link&gt;
  &lt;linkinfo&gt;To repair a reciprocating widget,
you must follow the instructions very carefully. Note
the sequence to follow. Do it.&lt;/linkinfo&gt;
&lt;/linklist&gt;</codeblock>
